div.div: Genjitsu Shugi Yuusha no Oukoku Saikenki

Suddenly summoned to a fantasy world and betrothed to the princess, Kazuya Souma is crowned the new king after providing the royal family with impressive advice. To rule the kingdom, he's taking the nontraditional (and very human) route of administrative reform. In a realm of dragons and elves, will this revolutionary's unique path prove effective?
(Source: Funimation)

How can you fall in love when you can’t even hold hands? Due to a childhood curse, anything that the Duke touches will die—which makes his flirty maid’s behavior all the more shocking! Is there a way for the Duke and his companions to somehow break the curse, or is he doomed to a life where love is forever out of his reach?
(Source: Funimation)

The story is about Ine and Shouzou, two pensioners well into their 80s who are mysteriously returned to their 20s one night. Note: Sixth place of Tsugimanga 2020 Award in the Web Manga Category Jiisan Baasan Wakagaeru is a web manga released on the author's pixiv and Twitter accounts, and later picked for print release by Kadokawa.
Yuusha no Yome ni Naritakute (￣∇￣) ゞ

I'm Berlina Lacotte, 18 years old. I've reincarnated into a fantasy world while retaining the memories of my previous life. Though I'm now an orphan, I'm able to live a satisfiying life in the city making use of the memories of my previous life as well the special skill I was given. One day, I met my soulmate. One of those guys commonly known as, "the hero." The instant I picked him out from the crowd, I knew it was meant to be. This was my was soulmate. A romantic comedy where the heroine is the pursuer. Note: Includes a side story.
